reviewText: Mr. Austin was one of the best...

A Great Video. Like the description promises. Mike Austin is teaching 10 different players his powerful swing with valuable tipps, instructions and all kind of tweaks you can imagine Just a little hand position correction can make the difference, increadible! I am using the DVD since two weeks and after some intense sessions on the driving range I was able to adjust my swing and gained some more average yards. Big recommendation!
